{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<blockquote>\n<p>Understanding Images on the Web</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3>Responsive Images</h3>\n<p><strong>display different images</strong> based on the <strong>user's device</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>problem</strong>: </p>\n<ul>\n<li>images have inherent dimensions, therefore <strong>cannot stretch</strong> beyond the width or length</li>\n<li><strong>retina screen</strong> displays require <strong>high resolution/large images</strong></li>\n<li>sending high-resolution images to <strong>standard displays and smaller devices</strong> is <strong>unnecessary data</strong> and a <strong>bad user experience</strong></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>things to consider</strong>:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>the <strong>device's dimension</strong></li>\n<li>the <strong>image's dimension</strong></li>\n<li>device's <strong>screen resolution</strong></li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Make Images Responsive</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>use SVG</strong> (vector-based images)</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>can <em>avoid the screen resolution problem</em></p>\n<ul>\n<li>bcuz browsers <em>automatically scale up SVGs for retina devices</em></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>make it <strong>fluid</strong>:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>set <code class=\"language-text\">width: 100%</code></li>\n<li>\n<p>and set max-width inline</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>img</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span>image<span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span>image.svg<span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span></span><span class=\"token style-attr language-css\"><span class=\"token attr-name\"> <span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">='</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token property\">max-width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 500px</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Raster Images</strong> (PNG, GIF, JPG) <strong>w/ Image Optimization</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>list alternative image files via <code class=\"language-text\">srcset</code></p>\n<ul>\n<li>use if image is <strong>smaller than 600px wide</strong></li>\n<li>1x: display for standard screens</li>\n<li>2x: display retina screens</li>\n<li>\n<p>older browser resort to <code class=\"language-text\">src</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>img</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span>illustration-small.png<span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span></span>\n<span class=\"token attr-name\">srcset</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span>images/illustration-small.png 1x,\n   images/illustration-big.png 2x<span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span></span><span class=\"token style-attr language-css\"><span class=\"token attr-name\">\n<span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">='</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token property\">max-width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 500px</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>specify a series of <code class=\"language-text\">sizes</code> of which images should be rendered</p>\n<ul>\n<li>use if image is <strong>larger than 600px wide</strong></li>\n<li>use <code class=\"language-text\">media queries</code> and<code class=\"language-text\">w</code> to define inherent widths of the images</li>\n<li>\n<p>this way, <em>can optimize data</em> to <em>even mobile retina screens</em> (which may only need standard images, rather than the retina images)</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>img</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span>photo-small.jpg<span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span></span>\n<span class=\"token attr-name\">srcset</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span>photo-big.jpg 2000w,\n     photo-small.jpg 1000w<span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span></span>\n<span class=\"token attr-name\">sizes</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span>(min-width: 960px) 960px,\n    100vw<span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- when the screen is larger than 960px wide, image is 960px --></span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- otherwise, image is 100vw (100% of viewport width) --></span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>change art direction w/ <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;picture&gt;</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;source&gt;</code></p>\n<ul>\n<li>use if <strong>feeling fancy</strong> w/ the designer</li>\n<li>use <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;picture&gt;</code> as a wrapper</li>\n<li>use <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;source&gt;</code> to conditionally load <em>differently cropped images</em> based on <em>media queries</em></li>\n<li>&#x3C; img/> is only specified for older browsers to use</li>\n<li>\n<p>but <em>loses retina optimization</em></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>picture</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>source</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">media</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span>(min-width: 401px)<span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">srcset</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span>photo-big.jpg<span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>source</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">media</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span>(max-width: 400px)<span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">srcset</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span>photo-tall.jpg<span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>img</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span>photo-small.jpg<span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>picture</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"path":"/frontend/10","title":"Frontend Focus 10 - Images on the Web","date":"2019-03-08","tags":["웹개발","프론트엔드","디자인","responsive design"]}}},"pageContext":{}}